<section class="row mb40">
  <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 tac">
    <h2 class="mb20">What Makes an Ethical Company?</h2>

    <div class="col-sm-3">
      <%= image_tag "icon_criteria_1.png" %>

      <p><strong>Environmental Impact</strong></p>

      <p>
        Carbon offsetting, paperless billing, investment in renewable energy - we consider anything that has an impact on the environment
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-3">
      <%= image_tag "icon_criteria_2.png" %>

      <p><strong>Value for Money</strong></p>

      <p>
        Are the prices fair? Are all of the costs transparent? We find you the best deals on products/services that have a positive impact
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-3">
      <%= image_tag "icon_criteria_3.png" %>

      <p><strong>Customer Experience</strong></p>

      <p>
        Are there hidden fees or lock-in contracts? Are they easy to contact and pleasant to talk to? We value the way a company treats 
        its customers
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-3">
      <%= image_tag "icon_criteria_4.png" %>

      <p><strong>Reputation &amp; Endorsements</strong></p>

      <p>
        What are people saying about the companies you buy from? Have they received endorsements from reputable sources? We like to find the 
        companies that have
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="clb"></div>
</section>